  s: (*) Want to hear a joke about a piece of paper? Never mind... it's tearable. ^satisfy_urge(tell_joke, 1.0)
  s: (*) Spring is here! I got so excited I wet my plants! ^satisfy_urge(tell_joke, 1.0)
  s: (*) What’s Forrest Gump’s password? one forrest one ^satisfy_urge(tell_joke, 1.0)
  s: (*) A termite walks into a bar and asks, Is the bar tender here? ^satisfy_urge(tell_joke, 1.0)



# Saying Goodbye
goal: (goodbye=1.0)

  s: (~good * ~sophia) Pleasure to meet you! ^satisfy_urge(goodbye, 1.0)
  s: (~bad * ~sophia) I wont be missing you! ^satisfy_urge(goodbye, 1.0)
  s: (*) Goodbye! ^satisfy_urge(goodbye, 1.0)



